channel.title: [422] Changing the connecting port
channel.description:
There's not much point in this unless you're gonna attempt to make a priv server with new deob but here goes.
Find
[code] Class53.anInt1242 = ((Class35.anInt866 ^ 0xffffffff) != -1 ? 40000 - -Class40.anInt1589 : 43594); [/code]
Change 43594 to the port you want
